Package utilities

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FileRWUtility
    A utility for writing a Collection of group elements to a text file, and for reading such a file to either a primitive array or to a List<G>, with G the appropriate Group implementation.
    GeneratingSetCatalog
    A collection of static methods that return generating sets for certain subgroups of the following three families of groups:
      (i) the General Linear Group on a finite dimensional vector space over a prime field,
     (ii) the Projective General Linear Group on a finite dimensional vector space over a prime field,
    (iii) the Symmetric Group on n letters.
    GenSetCatalog
    Reference: D.E.
    GroupOrderCalculator
    A collection of static methods for calculating the orders of certain finite groups, as well as the logarithms of the orders.
    LPSGeneratingSetUtility
    This class consists of a single static method, getLPSGenerators(short p, short q), which creates a List<PGL2_PrimeField> of size p+1 whose elements constitute a very special generating subset of PGL2(F_q) (or the subgroup PSL2(F_q), depending on whether or not p is a square mod q).
